portableDataExchange.serializer

Class PositionPdx

  • java.lang.Object
    • portableDataExchange.serializer.PositionPdx

  • public class PositionPdx
extends Object
    An example of a position object for a trading application. This class demonstrates serializing an object using the PdxSerializable interface.

    Since:
    6.6
    Author:
    GemStone Systems, Inc.
